metadata.name: Indifferent girl: Matilda
metadata.description:
This is genesis NFT of «Indifferent girls» collection.

Digital Painting 
Size: 3500*3500 pixel
300 DPI

Owner of the first NFT in collection will receive: 
additional full body NFT from the collection as a prize for winning auction (will be provided during 10 days after purchase). 

+ The collector also will get 3 original PNG file in 3500*3500 pixel in different color variations.

[About collection]

Sometimes life, people around you, unexpected circumstances force you to close. Fence yourself with a wall of indifferent eyes.
You have met them. And asked the question: what is behind it? 
Pain? 
Emptiness? 
Strength? 
Acceptance?
Or something completely different?
